abstract: John Ridsdel and Robert Hall of Canada, Kjartan Sekkingstad of Norway and unidentified Filipino woman are kidnapped from Oceanview Resort on Samal island, Mindanao, Philippines; no one has claimed responsibility.
lead_paragraph: Four people — two Canadian men, a Norwegian man and a Filipino woman — were abducted on Monday night from a resort on the southern Philippine island of Mindanao.

headline.print_headline: Asia; Philippines: Gunmen Abduct 4 People, Including 3 Foreigners, From Resort
